title: 2: MILFHUNTER
description:
Sofia tried crack! As if that wasn’t wild enough….we have the man, the myth, the legend—MILFHUNTER. Sofia and Milfhunter expose the truth behind the business, friendship, and show that was. The duo also discuss their newfound bond, how to deal with being fucked over, and once again, the accidental crack incident. Get your headphones on because you do NOT want your mom hearing this. But Milfhunter might :)
